<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٧٥٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5614">مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ زِيَادٍ: </a>أَنَّهُ سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«الْوَلَدُ لِصَاحِبِ الْفِرَاشِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>